<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract The article proposes close relations between the mature fiction of Machado de Assis and the critical thinking of Augusto Meyer. For this, it is worth not only Meyer&#8217;s essays, but also the memorialistic profile of his poetry.]]></p></abstract>
